HEADWORD: Antisocial
<hw>An`ti*so"cial</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Tending to
interrupt or destroy social intercourse; averse to society, or hostile
to its existence; <as>as, <ex>antisocial</ex> principles</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
